thread.title: Marcel Dupuis
thread.title_full: TENAQUIP Limited reviewed by Marcel Dupuis

author: Marcel Dupuis
title: Marcel Dupuis
text:
Lynn Donnelly provided prompt responses to my questions and helped set us up with an account so that we could get the items we required in a very short time span. She was very friendly, professional and courteous and I wouldn't hesitate to recommend both Tenaquip and Lynn to any of our stores in Kal Tire.
Marcel Dupuis
Assistant Manager Kal Tire Idylwyld Drive Saskatoon
